{"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"- ("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setContentInset:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@UIEdgeInsets","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"UIEdgeInsets"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"contentInset"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"animated:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"BOOL"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"animated"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"contentInset","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The new values to inset the content by.","type":"text"}]}]},{"name":"animated","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Specify ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"YES"},{"text":" if you want the map view to animate the change to","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the content inset or ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NO"},{"text":" if you want the map to inset the content","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"immediately.","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When the value of this property is equal to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIEdgeInsetsZero"},{"type":"text","text":", viewport"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"properties such as "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"centerCoordinate"},{"type":"text","text":" assume a viewport that matches the map"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"view’s frame. Otherwise, those properties are inset, excluding part of the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"frame from the viewport. For instance, if the only the top edge is inset, the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"map center is effectively shifted downward."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"When the map view’s superview is an instance of ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIViewController"},{"text":" whose","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"automaticallyAdjustsScrollViewInsets"},{"text":" property is ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"YES"},{"text":", the value of this","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"property may be overridden at any time.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The usage of ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"automaticallyAdjustsScrollViewInsets"},{"text":" has been deprecated","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"use the map view’s property ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/automaticallyAdjustsContentInset"},{"text":"instead.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To specify a completion handler to execute after the animation finishes, use"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the "},{"code":"-setContentInset:animated:completionHandler:","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" method."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/setContentInset:animated:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"metadata":{"fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setContentInset:animated:","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"tit